articles.title: Astrud Gilberto, bossa nova singer of The Girl from Ipanema, dies aged 83 - The Guardian
articles.description: Singer had no previous recording experience when she sang a defining song of Brazilian culture in 1963
articles.content:
Astrud Gilberto, whose dreamy interpretation of The Girl from Ipanema became the most popular version of the song, has died aged 83.
